---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Potensi Desa — Desa Sindangsari"
  description="Potensi Desa Sindangsari: pertanian, pariwisata, ekonomi kreatif, dan UMKM dataran tinggi yang siap dikembangkan."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="relative">
  <div class="h-48 sm:h-60 overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="/images/sawah_sindangsari.png"
      alt="Pertanian dan alam Desa Sindangsari"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: rgba(20,83,45,0.55);"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-end">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1152px] px-4 sm:px-6 w-full pb-6 text-white">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-white/80 flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Beranda</a>
        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        <span class="font-medium">Potensi Desa</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-extrabold mt-1">Potensi Desa Sindangsari</h1>
      <p class="text-white/85 mt-1 max-w-xl">Sumber daya dan peluang ekonomi yang menanti mitra & pembeli.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-[1152px] px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 space-y-6">

  <!-- Ekonomi Kreatif -->
  <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 items-stretch bg-white border border-line rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(16,35,26,.08)]">
    <a href="/potensi/ekraf" class="block aspect-[16/11] md:aspect-auto overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/kerupuk_tradisional.png"
        alt="Ekonomi Kreatif Desa Sindangsari"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </a>
    <div class="p-7">
      <span class="text-[13px] font-heading font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#E3F2E8] text-primary">Ekonomi Kreatif</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-extrabold text-primary mt-2">
        <a href="/potensi/ekraf" class="hover:underline">Ekonomi Kreatif & UMKM</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mt-2">Desa Sindangsari memiliki potensi ekonomi kreatif yang berkembang pesat. Industri rumah tangga mengolah bahan baku lokal menjadi makanan tradisional seperti opak, ranginang, kopi aren, dan keripik bonggol pisang.</p>
      <a href="/potensi/ekraf" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-4 text-accent font-heading font-semibold hover:underline">
        Selengkapnya <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Pertanian -->
  <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 items-stretch bg-white border border-line rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(16,35,26,.08)]">
    <a href="/potensi/pertanian" class="block aspect-[16/11] md:aspect-auto md:order-2 overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/kebun_sayur.png"
        alt="Pertanian dan perkebunan Desa Sindangsari"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </a>
    <div class="p-7 md:order-1">
      <span class="text-[13px] font-heading font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#E3F2E8] text-cta">Pertanian</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-extrabold text-primary mt-2">
        <a href="/potensi/pertanian" class="hover:underline">Pertanian & Perkebunan</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mt-2">Lahan desa yang berada di ketinggian 500-600 mdpl sangat subur untuk pertanian padi, jagung, singkong, serta buah-buahan seperti alpukat, durian, nangka, pisang, dan jeruk bali.</p>
      <a href="/potensi/pertanian" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-4 text-accent font-heading font-semibold hover:underline">
        Selengkapnya <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Pariwisata -->
  <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 items-stretch bg-white border border-line rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(16,35,26,.08)]">
    <a href="/potensi/pariwisata" class="block aspect-[16/11] md:aspect-auto overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/hero_sindangsari.png"
        alt="Wisata alam Desa Sindangsari"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </a>
    <div class="p-7">
      <span class="text-[13px] font-heading font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#D1FAE5] text-[#047857]">Pariwisata</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-extrabold text-primary mt-2">
        <a href="/potensi/pariwisata" class="hover:underline">Pariwisata Alam & Ekowisata</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mt-2">Keindahan alam pegunungan yang asri, udara yang sejuk, serta air terjun seperti Curug Masigit menawarkan potensi ekowisata alam terpadu berbasis pemberdayaan masyarakat lokal.</p>
      <a href="/potensi/pariwisata" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-4 text-accent font-heading font-semibold hover:underline">
        Selengkapnya <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-extrabold">Tertarik bermitra dengan Desa Sindangsari?</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 mt-2 max-w-xl mx-auto">Hubungi pemerintah desa untuk informasi investasi, kemitraan, atau kerja sama potensi desa.</p>
    <a href="/kontak" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-5 bg-white text-primary font-heading font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-sand transition-colors min-h-[44px]">
      <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Hubungi Desa
    </a>
  </div>

</main>

</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  setTimeout(() => { if (typeof lucide !== 'undefined') lucide.createIcons(); }, 300);
</script>
